    <ProductCard products={1} slot="featured" />
  </div>

  <p class="!mt-6">Have you ever wondered what makes great athletes tick?</p>
  <p>
    The Champion's Mind dives deep and reveals the training, motivation, thought
    processes and techniques elite-level athletes use to succeed. Whether it’s a
    marathon runner or an Olympic gold medalist, this book looks at how they
    stay focused on their goals and excel in their sport. It also explains the
    strategies they use to remain calm under pressure, make adjustments on the
    fly and maintain a strong competitive mindset.
  </p>
  <p>
    If you’re looking to become an elite athlete yourself or just want to gain
    insight into what makes champions tick, then this book is for you! You can
